text: Aladár von Farkas (20 October 1874 - 20 May 1949) was a Hungarian sports shooter. He competed in four events at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1874 births Category:1949 deaths Category:Hungarian male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Hungary Category:Shooters at the 1912 Summer Olympics
